OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1773850286
OL,3,CThree arrested after car driven onto
OL,4,Crailway line during police chase
OL,6,FThree people have been arrested after
OL,7,Fa car was driven onto a railway line
OL,8,Fand abandoned during a police chase.
OL,10,FTrains have been cancelled and
OL,11,Fdiverted today as a result of the
OL,12,Fincident, which forced the driver of a
OL,13,Ffreight train to make an emergency
OL,14,Fstop to avoid crashing into the car.
OL,16,FWiltshire Police say officers on
OL,17,Fpatrol last night were alerted to a
OL,18,Fsuspicious vehicle at about 1.30am on
OL,19,F17 March near Holt.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
