CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1773850286
OL,3,CThree arrested after car driven onto
OL,4,Crailway line during police chase
OL,6,FA spokesperson from the force said:
OL,7,F"When requested to stop the silver
OL,8,FVauxhall Insignia drove away, forced
OL,9,Fthrough multiple railway gates, and
OL,10,Fdrove onto a train line near Holt.
OL,12,F"The occupants decamped, and officers,
OL,13,Fincluding dog handlers attempted to
OL,14,Ftrack them. Suspected stolen property
OL,15,Ffrom a recent burglary was located in
OL,16,Fthe vehicle.
OL,18,F"A Mazda was stopped just after 3am in
OL,19,Fthe area and the three occupants were
OL,20,Farrested."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
