PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1773850286
OL,3,CThree arrested after car driven onto
OL,4,Crailway line during police chase
OL,6,FA 19-year-old man has now been
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving, failing to stop for an
OL,9,Fofficer, going equipped for theft and
OL,10,Ftheft of a pedal cycle.
OL,12,FA 17-year-old boy was arrested on
OL,13,Fsuspicion of failing to stop,
OL,14,Fdangerous driving, drug driving, going
OL,15,Fequipped for theft and theft of a
OL,16,Fpedal cycle.
OL,18,FAn 18-year-old woman was arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender and
OL,20,Fobstructing a police officer.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
