PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1773850286
OL,3,CThree arrested after car driven onto
OL,4,Crailway line during police chase
OL,6,FAll remain in custody for questioning.
OL,8,FBecause of the car being abandoned on
OL,9,Fthe rail track, train services on
OL,10,FTuesday 17 March aren't able to run
OL,11,Fbetween Trowbridge and Chippenham.
OL,12,FThat is affecting services between
OL,13,FSwindon and Westbury.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for GWR said: "A car
OL,16,Fhas been driven on to the line between
OL,17,FTrowbridge and Chippenham. Network
OL,18,FRail are making arrangements to have
OL,19,Fthe car removed, until this is done we
OL,20,Fare unable to run trains.
OL,26,@wD@^OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
